	</div>
	
</div></div><div class="sqs-block html-block" data-block-json="&#123;&quot;wysiwyg&quot;:&#123;&quot;engine&quot;:&quot;code&quot;,&quot;mode&quot;:&quot;htmlmixed&quot;,&quot;isSource&quot;:false,&quot;source&quot;:&quot;&quot;&#125;,&quot;html&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;--This post began as a small essay I wrote for the lovely group at &lt;a href=\&quot;https://uncommon.cc\&quot;&gt;Uncommon&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;(And you &lt;em&gt;really&lt;/em&gt; do want to &lt;a href=\&quot;/meet-the-horses\&quot;&gt;meet the horses&lt;/a&gt; at our Icelandic horse farm.)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;(Update: fixed the memorization graphic -- thought bubble didn't match the text)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Comments now closed.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&quot;,&quot;engine&quot;:&quot;visual&quot;&#125;" data-block-type="2" id="block-7c16d5a45e7a7ed4b0b3"><div class="sqs-block-content"><p><em>--This post began as a small essay I wrote for the lovely group at <a href="https://uncommon.cc">Uncommon</a>.&nbsp;</em></p><p>(And you <em>really</em> do want to <a href="/meet-the-horses">meet the horses</a> at our Icelandic horse farm.)&nbsp;</p><p>(Update: fixed the memorization graphic -- thought bubble didn't match the text)</p><p>Comments now closed.&nbsp;</p><p></p><p>&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div></div></div>
		 
  

              
